    "en": {
      "title": "Drug trafficker hacked to death in Orugodawatte",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st): A 34-year-old was brutally murdered close to the Orugodawatte Fly-Over on Monday (25) night.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said that two masked men had arrived in a luxury car, and brutally attacked the victim with sharp weapons.",
        "The man was ruled dead upon admission to Hospital, and it was reported that he was a resident of Meethotamulla.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said that investigations revealed that the deceased was connected to drug trafficking, and had two pending criminal cases filed against him",
        "IGP & Senior Cops failed to protect peaceful protestors \u2013 HRCSL"
      ],
